{"tid":1747942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽：呢個先係你要晨咁早去投票嘅原因","createTime":"2019-11-23T12:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T02:15:13.000Z","uid":181720,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb3f1272bebe4c226b331a4518a4eb8c5d5868a","tid":1747942,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v64kzgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv64kzgO.png&h=d01c43bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ki7usEv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKi7usEv.png&h=a3446192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遲啲去係真係會無得投<br />\n選票by definition 無記認 <br />\n唔會知邊個同你投咗<br />\n亦無可能揀返嗰張票出嚟<br />\n唔好再話咩早去會幫人配票<br />\n遲啲去你票都無埋呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c456bd6abb3f128de43e034ab252a5f0511df85","tid":1747942,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9574fda137486224f16e244059d315de03775a00","tid":1747942,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dc71ee08f1f0d1011a56524837d1d84fe96b59","tid":1747942,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0