：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"},{"pid":"adc8f0982024b8ad5fecac7ace75105d32321805","tid":1747942,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af43d6576d8dc7d15eb4dc5649d793b9f1f03bb","tid":1747942,"uid":6370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"d3f69683f814b08292f3ccde4fd2e16989704a93","tid":1747942,"uid":329122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159815d407fa3fad16dbf101a09074de4cc1f1ac","tid":1747942,"uid":5284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"唔推唔係人"},{"pid":"18615a36589b231804a5ea8dccf19eaf627cad7b","tid":1747942,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f53a05d29940185c1119d1b6db29ec6b9b70712","tid":1747942,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:14:05